Trinity::

She giggled," Yeah, I can twitch too. See?" and she stood up on her 
hind legs and giggled, wiggled and moved in a comical bout.  She 
landed on her feet and hugged Aerotaur. "Your invinkakle. No one can 
hurt you."

OOC: No it's not a typo, she's about 7 to 8 years old. So some 
vocabulary is still beyond her.
